biocode.fims.run

Class ProcessController

  • java.lang.Object
    • biocode.fims.run.ProcessController

  • public class ProcessController
extends java.lang.Object
    Tracks status of data validation. Helpful especially in a stateless environment. This class is meant to be read/written as an attribute for an HTTPSession when working in a Servlet environment.
